text: cng klaw theid muhammad “xallxh thrng ru di ying wa phwk khea phanak xyu nan theadı sahrab phraxngkh nan thrng ru sing phn yan wisay nı chan fa thanghlay læa phændin phraxngkh thrng hen chad læa thrng fang chad thuksingthukxyang mimi phu khumkhrxng dı sahrab phwk khea xun cak phraxngkh phraxngkh mi thrng rab ru phu dı khea rwm phakhi nı kar pkkhrxng khxng phraxngkh”
